    "htmlContent": "Share moments with your friends and followers like never before...\n\nBottleApp is original, FREE, fun to use and the latest generation of GPS location-based messaging...\n\nStep 1:  Choose to Post or Send\n•\tPOST a GPS Bottle on social media,\n•\tor SEND privately to contacts. \n\nStep 2:  Add contents: \n•\tText, Audio\n•\tPhotos, Videos\n•\tDocuments, Links\n\nStep 3:  Place the GPS Bottle on the map:\n•\tIt opens at your current location. Place it there, or scroll the globe to locate it anywhere.\n\nStep 4:  Location Condition:\n•\tGet people moving by adding an access radius…  or \n•\tSKIP this condition to allow it to be opened from anywhere.\n\nStep 5:  Time Condition:\n•\tSend your GPS Bottle into the future by adding a Time Window.\n•\tSet a challenge by adding a Countdown Timer…  or\n•\tSKIP this condition to allow it to be opened at any time at all.\n\nStep 6:  Edit, add Bottles, Post or Send\n•\tEdit your GPS Bottle,\n•\tadd another inside it to create a chain…  or\n•\tpress POST or SEND\n\nShare moments in time, and post them to the locations they took place: holiday snaps, childhood photos, places you lived or where you went to school.\n\nSet challenges, activities, and organise events: Treasure hunts, parties, pub crawls, and routes.\n\nPost promotional GPS Bottles with coupons inside. Work with influencers to generate footfall to your location or event.\n\n\nBottleApp Premium (One Year Subscription)\n\nWhen you become Premium your payment will be charged to your iTunes account. Your subscription automatically renews unless you cancel it at least 24 hours before your next renewal date. You can cancel or manage your subscription in your iTunes account settings.\n\nhttps://www.bottleappmessenger.app/about-5\nhttps://www.bottleappmessenger.app/terms",
